traitblender-*.zip
PLAN.md

# MkDocs build output (regenerated locally; CI builds for GitHub Pages)
traitblender/site/

# =============================================================================
# RELEASE CHECKLIST — TraitBlender version (currently 2.3.0)
# Search/replace 2.3.0 → X.Y.Z and v2.3.0 → vX.Y.Z unless noted below.
# =============================================================================

# --- Addon package (extension build version; keep both in sync) ---
# traitblender/blender_manifest.toml
#   version = "X.Y.Z"
# build_zips/blender_manifest.template.toml
#   version = "X.Y.Z"

# --- CITATION.cff ---
# CITATION.cff
#   version: X.Y.Z
#   date-released: "YYYY-MM-DD"
#   identifiers → description: "... version X.Y.Z."
#   identifiers → value: https://github.com/Imageomics/TraitBlender/releases/tag/vX.Y.Z
#   doi: (update if Zenodo publishes a new record/DOI for this release)

# --- Zenodo (.zenodo.json; validated by .github/workflows/validate-zenodo.yaml) ---
# .zenodo.json
#   "version": "X.Y.Z"
#   "publication_date": "YYYY-MM-DD"
# Also create/publish the matching version on https://zenodo.org (GitHub–Zenodo integration
# or manual upload). Keep CITATION.cff doi in sync with the Zenodo record you cite.

# --- Root README ---
# README.md
#   Intro line: **vX.Y.Z**
#   CLI example: traitblender-vX.Y.Z-linux.zip
#   Zenodo badge/link DOI URLs if the Zenodo record ID changes

# --- Documentation (MkDocs source: traitblender/docs/) ---
# traitblender/docs/index.md
#   About section: **TraitBlender vX.Y.Z**
#   BibTeX block: version = {vX.Y.Z}
#   BibTeX block: doi = {...}  (if Zenodo DOI changed)
#
# traitblender/docs/getting-started/installation.md
#   Supported versions table: **vX.Y.Z**
#   CLI install example: traitblender-vX.Y.Z-linux.zip
#   Download step: latest release (**vX.Y.Z**)
#   Troubleshooting: **TraitBlender vX.Y.Z**
#
# traitblender/docs/getting-started/quick-start.md
#   Prerequisites: **TraitBlender vX.Y.Z**

# --- GitHub release (not edited in repo; do on publish) ---
# Create release tag vX.Y.Z on GitHub (triggers .github/workflows/release-zips.yml).
#   Assets are named: traitblender-vX.Y.Z-windows.zip, ...-mac.zip, ...-linux.zip,
#   ...-linux-headless.zip
# .github/workflows/release-zips.yml
#   Comment example tag (line ~2): vX.Y.Z

# --- Do NOT change for a TraitBlender-only version bump ---
# traitblender/blender_manifest.toml → blender_version_min (Blender floor, e.g. 5.1.0)
# requirements-wheels.txt, requirements-wheels-headless.txt
# traitblender/wheels/*.whl
# CITATION.cff → cff-version (Citation File Format spec, not TraitBlender)
# blender_manifest.toml → schema_version
